### 🚀 Articles API - Complete Test Suite

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:5212/api/Test/health

### 2. Get Test Credentials
GET http://localhost:5212/api/Test/login-test

### 3. Generate JWT Token for Testing
GET http://localhost:5212/api/Test/jwt-test

### 4. Login with Credentials
POST http://localhost:5212/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 5. Test Authentication Info (No Auth Required)
GET http://localhost:5212/api/Test/auth-info

### 6. Test Protected Endpoint (Replace TOKEN_HERE with actual token)
GET http://localhost:5212/api/Test/protected
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### 7. Validate Token via GET (Replace TOKEN_HERE with actual token)
GET http://localhost:5212/api/Auth/validate
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### 8. Validate Token via POST (Replace TOKEN_HERE with actual token)
POST http://localhost:5212/api/Auth/validate
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### 9. Validate Token via Header (Replace TOKEN_HERE with actual token)
POST http://localhost:5212/api/Auth/validate-header
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### 10. Test Token Validation via Test Controller (Replace TOKEN_HERE with actual token)
GET http://localhost:5212/api/Test/validate-token
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### 11. Get All Articles (Public)
GET http://localhost:5212/api/Articles

### 12. Get Article by ID (Public)
GET http://localhost:5212/api/Articles/1

### 13. Get Article by Title (Protected - Replace TOKEN_HERE with actual token)
GET http://localhost:5212/api/Articles/title/Getting%20Started%20with%20ASP.NET%20Core%208
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### 14. Get Articles by Tag (Public)
GET http://localhost:5212/api/Articles/tag/aspnet

### 15. Get Published Articles (Public)
GET http://localhost:5212/api/Articles/published

### 16. Get All Newspapers (Public)
GET http://localhost:5212/api/Newspapers

### 17. Get Newspaper by ID (Public)
GET http://localhost:5212/api/Newspapers/1

### 18. Get Newspaper by Name (Public)
GET http://localhost:5212/api/Newspapers/name/tech%20daily

### 19. Get Active Newspapers (Public)
GET http://localhost:5212/api/Newspapers/active

### 20. Create New Article (Protected - Replace TOKEN_HERE with actual token)
POST http://localhost:5212/api/Articles
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New Test Article",
  "content": "This is a test article content",
  "author": "Test Author",
  "tags": ["test", "api"],
  "isPublished": true,
  "newspaperId": 1
}

### 21. Create New Newspaper (Protected - Replace TOKEN_HERE with actual token)
POST http://localhost:5212/api/Newspapers
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Newspaper",
  "description": "A test newspaper",
  "website": "https://testnewspaper.com",
  "isActive": true
}

### 22. Update Article (Protected - Replace TOKEN_HERE with actual token)
PUT http://localhost:5212/api/Articles/1
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Article Title",
  "content": "Updated content",
  "author": "Updated Author",
  "tags": ["updated", "test"],
  "isPublished": true,
  "newspaperId": 1
}

### 23. Update Newspaper (Protected - Replace TOKEN_HERE with actual token)
PUT http://localhost:5212/api/Newspapers/1
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Newspaper",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "website": "https://updatednewspaper.com",
  "isActive": true
}

### 24. Delete Article (Protected - Replace TOKEN_HERE with actual token)
DELETE http://localhost:5212/api/Articles/1
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### 25. Delete Newspaper (Protected - Replace TOKEN_HERE with actual token)
DELETE http://localhost:5212/api/Newspapers/1
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### 26. Get Articles by Newspaper (Public)
GET http://localhost:5212/api/Articles/newspaper/1

### 27. S3 Test (Public)
GET http://localhost:5212/api/Test/s3-test

